---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Ginger Island Survival — Wenji Makes" description="A Stardew Valley survival overhaul: wake up stranded on Ginger Island and earn your way back to the mainland.">
  <div class="mod-header"><div class="container">
    <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:16px;"><span class="tag">Overhaul</span><span class="tag">Story</span><span class="tag">Survival</span><span class="tag">Ginger Island</span></div>
    <h1>Ginger Island Survival</h1>
    <p class="meta">1.0.0 · SMAPI 4.0+ · Custom Farm Loader · Mod ID: 46543</p>
  </div></div>
  <section class="mod-content container">
    <img src="https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/1303/images/headers/46543_1779461570.jpg" alt="Ginger Island Survival" class="mod-image-full" />
    <p><strong>You don’t start on a farm. You wake up on the shore of Ginger Island with nothing but a washed-up crate.</strong></p>
    <p>This overhaul changes the opening of Stardew Valley. Explore the island, gather resources, build a temporary camp, survive from scratch, and gradually earn your way back to the mainland.</p>
    <p>Core features:</p>
    <ul style="color:var(--text-muted);margin:12px 0 24px 20px;">
      <li>A new opening that replaces the traditional farm tutorial</li>
      <li>Island survival, resource management, and camp building</li>
      <li>Original story events, including pirate raids</li>
      <li>Multiple ways to earn your return to the mainland</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;margin:32px 0 12px;">Installation</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-mono);background:var(--bg-card);padding:12px 16px;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:0.9rem;border:1px solid var(--border);">Requires SMAPI 4.0+ and Custom Farm Loader.<br />Extract both downloaded folders into your Stardew Valley <code>Mods/</code> directory.</p>
    <div style="margin-top:40px;display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;"><a href="https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/46543" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">Download on Nexus Mods</a><a href="/en/mods" class="btn btn-outline">← Back to Mods</a></div>
    <div style="margin-top:48px;padding:20px;background:var(--bg-card);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--border);">
      <p style="font-weight:600;margin-bottom:4px;">Ginger Island Survival expansion</p>
      <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.9rem;">I’m expanding this mod into a larger paid edition with more story content, maps, and gameplay systems.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
